==English==
===Noun===
'''composition'''
#The [[combining]] of [[different]] [[part]]s to make a [[whole]].
#The [[general]] [[makeup]] of something.
#A [[mixture]] or [[compound]]; the [[result]] of [[composing]]
#A [[work]] of [[music]], [[literature]] or [[art]].
#An [[essay]].
#{''Linguistics'') The [[formation]] of [[compound]] [[word]]s from [[separate]] words.
#(''Printing'') [[Typesetting]].

